...@_theme

direction: right

Backlog.class: pill-card
Ready.class: pill-card
"In Progress".class: pill-card
Validation.class: pill-card
Review.class: pill-card
Merged.class: merged-card
Closed.class: closed-card
Blocked.class: blocked-card

Backlog -> Ready: {class: primary-flow}
Ready -> "In Progress": linked PR {class: primary-flow}
"In Progress" -> Validation: tests, docs,\nmetadata, evidence {class: primary-flow}
Validation -> Review: ready for review {class: primary-flow}
Review -> Merged: PR merged {class: primary-flow}
Merged -> Closed: issue closed {class: primary-flow}

"In Progress" -> Blocked: {class: secondary-flow}
Blocked -> "In Progress": {class: secondary-flow}
